reviews.review_text:
Listen to the River Surprised no one has reviewed Holbrook City Island 84. Great capture of a fun night! Saw both years here (listened to 6.22.83 last night!). 
Check out Black Peter, hot w/ cool harmonies in end. Not the greatest show but good moments and a good party on a great summer tour!
